### Hanu Ji API Tests
### Install "REST Client" extension in VS Code to run these

@base = http://localhost:3000
@agent = http://localhost:3001
@webhook = http://localhost:3002

### ── Auth ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Login / Register
# @name login
POST {{base}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "test_user_001",
  "name": "Test User",
  "channel": "web"
}

###

@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### ── User ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get Profile
GET {{base}}/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Profile
PUT {{base}}/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Raj Sharma",
  "timezone": "Asia/Kolkata",
  "work_start": "09:00",
  "work_end": "18:00"
}

### Get Conversations
GET {{base}}/api/users/conversations?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── Memory ────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get All Memories
GET {{base}}/api/memory
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── Analytics ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get Summary
GET {{base}}/api/analytics/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Daily Stats
GET {{base}}/api/analytics/daily
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ── Agent Direct ───────────────────────────────────────────

### Test Agent — General
POST {{agent}}/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "test_user_001",
  "channel": "web",
  "message": "Hello! What can you do?"
}

### Test Agent — Calendar Fetch
POST {{agent}}/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "test_user_001",
  "channel": "web",
  "message": "What's on my calendar today?"
}

### Test Agent — Create Event
POST {{agent}}/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "test_user_001",
  "channel": "web",
  "message": "Schedule a team standup tomorrow at 10am for 30 minutes"
}

### ── Health Checks ──────────────────────────────────────────

### API Gateway Health
GET {{base}}/health

### Agent Service Health
GET {{agent}}/health

### Webhook Service Health
GET {{webhook}}/health
